name: Facebook Duct Tape
description:
There was a video posted on YouTube about "25 Things I Hate About Facebook." In that video, he mentions he'd like to cover the whole sidebar with duct tape, so I decided to make it so.

Be warned, this script will make that sidebar on the homepage useless. But isn't it already?

Duct tape picture source: http://www.sxc.hu/photo/586526 Credit: vivre
css:
/*************************************
Script & image by Paul Conigliaro, 2009.

This will make your sidebar on the
Facebook homepage useless.

But isn't it already?

Duct tape picture source:
http://www.sxc.hu/photo/586526
Credit: vivre

http://conigs.com
http://iamawesome.net
*************************************/

@-moz-document domain("facebook.com") {

.UITwoColumnLayout_NarrowContent * {display:none !important;}

.UITwoColumnLayout_NarrowContent {display:block !important; width:320px !important; height:807px !important; background: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,) no-repeat !important;}

}
